<span id="freeTextContainer13715417303985751190">Mother.<br/><br/>Though this book is a communist propaganda, one cannot simply sideline this book naming so. It was slow and boring at times but the reality brought out by Maxim gorky was outstanding. The art of realism was at its best. The character development of &apos;The Mother&apos; was just awe. The way Gorky have portray the struggle of the working class from the perspective of a mother, was just awesome. <br/><br/>Recommend for people who love realistic literature, who starve to learn how the world functions.<br/>Definite</span>
  <span id="freeText13715417303985751190" style="display:none">Mother.<br /><br />Though this book is a communist propaganda, one cannot simply sideline this book naming so. It was slow and boring at times but the reality brought out by Maxim gorky was outstanding. The art of realism was at its best. The character development of 'The Mother' was just awe. The way Gorky have portray the struggle of the working class from the perspective of a mother, was just awesome. <br /><br />Recommend for people who love realistic literature, who starve to learn how the world functions.<br />Definitely not for people who love fantasy literature or who read to pass time.</span>
